{"tid":2324221,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Airbnb定價每股68美元　美IPO規模直逼2000年科網泡沫","createTime":"2020-12-13T19:10:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T08:16:53.000Z","uid":295230,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"af7919349628f423943788dbc8ffccb1880179f7","tid":2324221,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T19:10:19.000Z","msg":"短租住宿網站Airbnb宣布將其IPO價格定在每股68美元，預計將於12月10日在納斯達克全球精選市場開始交易。據報，其定價超出指導價區間高端，籌集資金約35億美元。<br />\n<br />\n短租住宿網站Airbnb宣布將其IPO價格定在每股68美元，預計將於12月10日在納斯達克全球精選市場開始交易。據報，其定價超出指導價區間高端，籌集資金約35億美元。<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n按這一價格計算，該公司完全攤薄估值達到約470億美元，其中包括員工股票期權和限制性股票單位。<br />\n據統計美國交易所今年IPO的累計融資規模已超過1,630億美元，宗數達420宗，其中包括DoorDash規模33.7億美元的上市交易，規模直逼2000年互聯網泡沫時的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ac991ea3404997b761f27381440a865f7deee1","tid":2324221,"uid":131884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T19:52:33.000Z","msg":"懷疑根本無人識得為依家啲妖股估值"},{"pid":"44f3b2d10af975bb4fbeae7c8df6bbf321958445","tid":2324221,"uid":182334,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T01:44:03.000Z","msg":"歷史會重覆"},{"pid":"611831e1bba178501fe4956f698b172fe6b6f608","tid":2324221,"uid":89225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T02:21:06.000Z","msg":"直逼科網泡沫講左幾多年"},{"pid":"437c1fdaa11f5b7c351011d1dabb562987f726ac","tid":2324221,"uid":230146,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T02:31:17.000Z","msg":"不斷印銀紙，<br />\n泡沫點爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0fe1bfe6f11c671b576b3b488d25cbdbb6dab0","tid":2324221,"uid":90077,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T0